  "message": "Add rust-toolchain.toml to pin nightly toolchain\n\nPin the project to the nightly Rust toolchain channel with rustfmt and\nclippy components. This ensures all developers and CI environments use\na consistent toolchain, preventing build inconsistencies from toolchain\nversion drift.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
